Frank Felton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Felton 0 Frank Felton (April 4, 1906 in Hartford, Connecticut – 1957) was an actor and from 1942 to 1957 performed in dozens of Hollywood movies and television shows. He died in 1957, in Los Angeles, at the age of 51.
